r restoring force (`c1*x0`), linear damping (`c2*x1`), nonlinear stiffness (`c3`, `c6`, etc.), nonlinear damping/fractional powers (`c10`).\n- This skeleton can be trained or fitted by adjusting the parameters to match observed data.']
